Package: daphniaruler
Type: Package
Title: Measure morphometric traits of zooplankton from images
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nelson Stevens
Maintainer: Nelson Stevens <nelson.stevens92@gmail.com>
Description: This package automatically measures body size, tail length, 
    tail angle from daohnia or other zooplankton species. For daphnia it's also
    possible to detect the eye enabling a more precise measurement of body size.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    reticulate,
    stringr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    vdiffr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
URL: https://nelstevens.github.io/daphniaRuler
VignetteBuilder: knitr
